<h2>Step Into Light. Walk in Truth.</h2>
<p>
WalkWay Kakuma is a Christ-centered outreach ministry serving Kakuma and Kalobeyei refugee communities. We bring hope, discipleship, and support through evangelism, home visits, prayer gatherings, children outreach, and care for the sick and vulnerable.
</p>
<a class="btn" href="#about">Learn More</a>
