<section id="about">
<div class="section-title">
<h2>About WalkWay Kakuma</h2>
</div>
<p style="max-width:800px;margin:auto;text-align:center;">
WalkWay Kakuma is dedicated to walking alongside individuals and families facing hardship, restoring faith, and sharing the love of Christ. Through structured outreach and community engagement, we help people experience transformation and hope even in challenging circumstances.
</p>
</section>

<section class="mission">
<div class="section-title">
<h2>Our Mission</h2>
